&lt;h1 id="were-at-the-beginning-of-an-infinity-of-knowledge"&gt;We’re at the Beginning of an Infinity of Knowledge&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mar 15 2021&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;
The difference with &lt;em&gt;The Beginning of Infinity&lt;/em&gt; is you&amp;rsquo;re getting a worldview. You&amp;rsquo;re not getting the standard take from physicists about how to understand quantum theory. You&amp;rsquo;re not getting the standard take of how to understand knowledge from philosophers. And you&amp;rsquo;re certainly not getting the standard take of how to understand mathematics from mathematicians.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Read the Best 100 Books Over and Over Again</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again/</link><pubDate>Wed, 10 Mar 2021 19:05:24 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
