&lt;h1 id="read-the-best-100-books-over-and-over-again"&gt;Read the Best 100 Books Over and Over Again&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mar 10 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Many claim to read, but very few understand&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;The Beginning of Infinity&lt;/em&gt; reminds me the most of &lt;em&gt;Gödel, Escher, Bach&lt;/em&gt; in that it is very wide-ranging and stitches together ideas from many different disciplines. It&amp;rsquo;s very difficult to understand and follow completely. Everyone claims to have read it, but, as far as I can tell, very few people understand it.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Specific Knowledge Is Highly Creative or Technical</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/specific-knowledge-is-highly-creative-or-technical/</link><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2019 16:57:30 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/naval/orig/specific-knowledge-is-highly-creative-or-technical/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/specific-knowledge-is-highly-creative-or-technical.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
